{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "第二回 绝地惊艳\n\n柳鹤亭与翠装少女被困地道，门户突闭，黑暗中翠装少女失踪。白衣女子陶纯纯从秘道出现，自称是石观音师妹，无恨大师弟子。两人互生情愫，陶纯纯揭示秘屋机关秘密。\n\n东宫太子项煌带神刀将军胜奎英、铁锏将军尉迟高闯入，自称南荒大君之子。项煌对陶纯纯心生觊觎，与柳鹤亭产生冲突。柳鹤亭展现身手，夺刀示威。\n\n众人离开秘屋，发现林中惨状：入云龙金四被砍断一手一足，惨死树下，临死紧握黑色碎布与赤色须发。银衫少女被点穴绑于树上。金四死前断续说出\"想不到……他们……我的……\"，真相成谜。\n\n柳鹤亭悲愤交加，誓言为金四复仇。他携碎布与赤须，狂掠至沂山深处，心潮翻涌。秋夜荒山中，忽闻神秘叹息与厌世低语，一条淡灰人影凌空而立，似在悬枝自尽。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_cui_zhuang_shao_nv",
      "text": "这栋房子里看来像是渺无人踪，以姑娘所见，那'石观音'会走到哪里去了呢？多年来进入此间的武林人士，从未有一人生返，若说俱都是被那'石观音'一一杀死，那么你我此刻怎地见不到她的踪影？若说那'石观音'根本不在这里，那么，这武林豪士却又是被谁杀死的呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_zhuang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "翠装少女",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "我现在心乱得很，你看是有什么话要问我，等一会儿再说好吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_cui_zhuang_shao_nv",
      "text": "姑娘，这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_zhuang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "翠装少女",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "这是怎么回事？这扇门是谁关上的？怎么会开不开了？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_zhuang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "翠装少女",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "这是怎么回事？我……我也不知道。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_cui_zhuang_shao_nv",
      "text": "你的那柄剑呢？拿出来试试，也许能将这扇大门刺穿！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_zhuang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "翠装少女",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "呀！我又忘了它了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_zhuang_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "翠装少女",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "呀！我大概是把它忘记在……方才那个床上了。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我去找找！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_cui_zhuang_shao_nv",
      "text": "你……姑娘，你在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你在哪里？你在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然开了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "想不到你在这里。我真担心她会把你杀死。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "我师姐自幼娇纵，做什么事都任性得很，她要是……她要是想害死你，其实也没有什么恶意，希望你能原谅她。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "在下已入绝境，多谢姑娘相救……",
      "tone": "感激",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "你不用谢我，我知道这些事都是我师姐做出来的，我帮忙你，不是很应该的吗？唉－－我真不懂，她为什么常常要杀死与她根本无冤无仇的人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "姑娘的师姐，可就是那位'南海仙子'石琪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "师父他老人家去世之后，我就没有和她见过面，却不知道这些年来，她……她竟变了，我一直在山上守着师父的墓，直到最近才知道她在这里，所以……我就来找她。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "我一到了这里，就听见你在吹箫，那箫声，我……我从来也没有听过。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "只要姑娘愿意，在下以后可以随时吹给姑娘听的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "我本来要进去找师姐，可是听到你的箫声，我像是什么都忘了！",
      "tone": "陶醉",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "后来那鼓声响起，接着又有一道剑光将那些鼓一齐划破，我认得那道剑光就是师父她老人家昔年佩着避邪的'避魔龙吟剑'，所以我知道那是师姐到了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "这房子本来是师父昔年的一位故友所建的，我幼时曾经来过，知道这房子满处都是机关，所以我看见你贸然走进来的时候，心里着急得很，正想……正想着进来看看，哪知这时我师姐也跟着进去了，我想起我听到的武林中有关我师姐的种种传说，心里就更着急了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "我知道这一下你必然会遇着危险，但是我又不愿和师姐当面冲突，我……我想了许久，只好从这房子后面一条秘道中进来，我虽然以前来过这里，也从那位前辈那里知道了一些这屋子的秘密，可是毕竟过了这么多年，我找了许久，才找到这条秘道，又找丁许久，才找到这里。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "我担心你此刻已被师姐杀了，哪知……却在这里遇着了你。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "想起来，已经许多年了，我和师姐都没有见过面，不知道她现在变成什么样子？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "唉！我知道她不会变的，她永远像个年轻的女孩子一样。是不是？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "正是。令师姐能令芳华永驻，难道她知道什么驻颜之术吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "这个－－我以后再告沂你。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "姑娘虽然得知此屋的秘径，想必也能将这里的扇门户打开了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "让我试试看！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "想不到十年来这里门户的枢纽仍然一点也没有改变。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "白衣女子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "这不是我那柄'龙吟剑'吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来诸葛先生的神算，亦不过如此，我早就知道秘屋左近必有秘道，却想不到竟被奎英误打误撞地发现了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我当是谁？原来是吹箫郎君已先我而入了，好极－－呀，还有位风流美貌的娘子，好极，奎英快举高火把，让我看个仔细。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "在下等与阁下素不相识，还望阁下出言尊重些，免得彼此伤了和气！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_kui_ying",
      "speaker_name": "胜奎英",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "你可知道你在面对何人说话，在太子面前竟敢如此……哼哼1……我看你真是活得起腻了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无妨，无妨，不知者不罪，又怎能怪得了人家？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_sheng_kui_ying",
      "text": "奎英，你常说当今武林，没有高手，如今你且看看这两位，一位身怀神剑，轻功更是妙绝，一位虽未现出武功，但却已能以箫音克敌，内功想必更是惊人！哈哈，难道这两人还不能算是武林高人！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位身手如此高明，不知可否将大名、师承见告？先让我听听中州武林高人的名号。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "在下贱名不足挂齿，倒是阁下的姓名，在下是极想听听的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_sheng_kui_ying",
      "text": "我足迹初涉中州，也难怪他们不认得我，奎英，你先莫动怒，且将我的姓名说给他们听听又有何妨。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_kui_ying",
      "speaker_name": "胜奎英",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sheng_kui_ying",
      "speaker_name": "胜奎英",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "尔等听清，此刻与尔等谈话之人，乃'南荒大君'陛下之东宫太子，尔等如再有无理情事－－",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "娘子，你笑些什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "我觉得很有意思。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "是极，是极，很有意思。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "如此有意思的事，你为何不笑？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "是什么事有意思，你们笑些什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "我也不知是什么事有意思，但娘子说是有意思，自然是有意思的了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "我与你素不相识，你也不必问我的名字，你那八面皮鼓，也不是我划破的，我只觉得你名字竟然叫做'太子'，是以才觉得很有意思！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "我叫陶纯纯，你不要告诉别人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "我那八面'天雷神鼓'，真的不是你划破的吗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "我从来没有说过骗人的话，难道你还不信？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "但你手中的这柄利剑，哪里来的？哼－－奎英，你知不知道有些人口中虽说从不说谎，但其实说谎说得最多。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "纵是说谎，便又怎地？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "我与这位姑娘之间的事情，我看你还是少管些的好。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "这位便是'南荒大君'殿前的'神刀将军'胜奎英，嘿嘿，河南的'胜家刀法'，你想必早就知道的了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "这位'铁锏将军'尉迟高，在中原武林，虽然声名较弱，但是－－嘿嘿，'关内一条鞭，赛过活神仙，关外两根锏，艺高九云天。'这句话你大约听人说过，至于我－－",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "这柄剑虽然是方才划破你那八面皮鼓的剑，可是使剑的人却不是我，唉－－你要是再不相信，我……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "娘子既如此说，我自然是相信的，但是使剑的人此刻在哪里，娘子想必是一定知道的了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "这使剑的人究竟到哪里去了，我也不知道，她也许在这地道外面，也许在别的地方，唉－－也许她就在这地道里面也不一定，只是她虽看得见我们，我们却再也看不到她。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 620,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "难道此人便是那'石观音'么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "娘子你也未免说得太过了，想那'石观音'武功虽然高明，却也不是神仙，何况－－",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我倒要看看她究竟是否真有三头六臂，竟敢－－哼哼！竟敢将人命视如草芥。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也正要去找她。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这条好像就是通向外面的出路！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "你站在这里干什么？难道你不出去么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 646
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "我自然要出去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "我只当你不敢去哩！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "前面似已无路可行，难道那－－",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "原来你对此间的设置倒熟悉得很。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "我当然知道啦，那'石观音'就是我的师姐，只不过我已有许多许多年没有见过她了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "难道你亦是那'无恨大师'的弟子？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "你倒也知道我师父的名字！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_sheng_kui_ying",
      "text": "难怪河南胜家神刀名扬四海，这'紫金鱼鳞'，果真是口宝刀。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_sheng_kui_ying",
      "text": "奎英，什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 706
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "没有什么，只不过在下将胜将军的宝刀借来看了一看而已。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 710
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他这口刀真是不凡，以后有机会，我也要借来看一看的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "以后－－以后自然会有机会的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里想必就是出口了吧？由此上去，不知是否－－",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 722,
      "line_end": 724
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "不错，这里上去就是那栋秘屋，方才在下就是由此处下来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "此处既是出口，那么就请娘子你先上去吧。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 732
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么我就不客气，要先上去了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 740
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好极，好极，想来古之聂隐红泉，亦不过如此吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "你要是上不来的话，就从旁边的钢枝爬上来好了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "正是，正是，若没有这些钢枝，我还真上不去哩。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 758
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_sheng_kui_ying",
      "text": "两位你说可是？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 758,
      "line_end": 760
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位先请，在下殿后。",
      "tone": "谦逊",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好身手。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_yu_chi_gao",
      "text": "此次该轮到阁下了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_yu_chi_gao",
      "text": "火把在这里。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "喂，你在看什么呀？这里果然一个人也没有，我师姐又不知跑到哪里去了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 802,
      "line_end": 806
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "你要是没有见过蜡烛，我倒可以送你一些，让你也好日夜观赏。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 808,
      "line_end": 810
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": "char_xiang_huang",
      "text": "人家才不是没有见过蜡烛哩。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 814,
      "line_end": 814
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "speaker_name": "陶纯纯",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "我们再往前面看看，你快些来呀！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 816,
      "line_end": 816
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_huang",
      "speaker_name": "东宫太子",
      "listener": "char_tao_chun_chun",
      "text": "纯纯，那少年和你……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 820,
      "line_end": 820
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_jin_si",
      "text": "金兄。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 878,
      "line_end": 880
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "speaker_name": "柳鹤亭",
      "listener": "char_jin_si",
      "text": "金兄，振作些！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 886,
      "line_end": 886
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_si",
      "speaker_name": "入云龙",
      "listener": "char_liu_he_ting",
      "text": "想……不到……他……他们……我的……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 886,
      "line_end": 886
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 900,
      "line_end": 900
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唉！人生为什么如此枯燥，死了……死了……死了也好。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 1000,
      "line_end": 1000
    }
  ],
